The Talk - The Love Boat Reunion
Nov 5 - 2013


More than three decades after the Love Boat first set sail on ABC and more than two decades after it made its final voyage the cast reunited for a very special episode of The Talk.
The former costars reminisced about their time together in the 1970s and 80s. The Love Boat aired for 10 seasons between 1977 and 1986 and spawned 4 additional specials.
